      "content": "ugh just tripped while running and my ankle is super swollen. its hurting a lot and i cant really put any weight on it at all without it feeling like it's gonna give out. i think i just sprained it though, should i just do the RICE thing (rest, ice, compression, elevation) for a few days and see if it gets better?",
