      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'm just worried about the doctor thing cuz clinic wait times in vancouver are a nightmare right now and it's kinda expensive if it's not an emergency. you're pretty sure it's just a sprain then? if i just take some ibuprofen and do the ice thing, i should be fine to just stay home for most of the week, right?",
