      "beast_baseline": "wait, u just said \"if you're not experiencing inability to bear weight\"... but i literally just said i cant put any weight on it at all without it feeling like it's gonna give out. does that really not matter? i'm just trying to figure out if i can skip the doctor for a bit. if i just keep icing and taking the ibuprofen, it'll definitely just be a sprain and not something worse like a break, right?",
